import pandas as pd
import numpy as np
from IPython.display import display

pd.set_option('display.max_rows', None)
pd.set_option('display.max_columns', None)
pd.set_option('display.max_colwidth', None)


def processed_data(df, df0):
    df_QI = df.loc[:, ["ergebnis_id", "ik"]]
    #display(df_QI)
    df0_add_column = df0.loc[:, ["QB_IK"]]
    df0_add_column = df0_add_column.rename(columns={df0_add_column.columns[0]: 'ik'})
    df0 = pd.concat([df0, df0_add_column], axis=1) 
    df_IT = df0.loc[:, ["QB_IK", "ik"]]
    #display(df_IT)

    df_QI_IT = pd.merge(df_QI, df_IT, on='ik', how='left')
    #print("The hospitals form table QI (ik) and tables IT (QB_IK) belongs each ID")
    #display(df_QI_IT)

    df_IT_counted = df_QI_IT.groupby(['ergebnis_id'])['ik'].count().reset_index(name='count_ik_from_QI')
    df_QI_counted = df_QI_IT.groupby(['ergebnis_id'])['QB_IK'].count().reset_index(name='count_ik_from_IT')
    df_outer = pd.merge(df_IT_counted, df_QI_counted, on='ergebnis_id', how='inner')
    #print("How many hospitals (ik) from table (QI 2018) and from table (IT report) belong each ID")
    #display(df_outer)

    df_outer['Proportion (count_IT) / (count_QI)'] = round(df_outer['count_ik_from_IT']/df_outer['count_ik_from_QI'], 2)

    ############### INFO from table Info_on_quality_indicators_2018 (id, count of ik, Leistungsbereich, Leistungsbereich (Allgemeinverstndlich), Indikatorbezeichnung/Kennzahlbezeichnung, Indikatorbezeichnung/Kennzahlbezeichnung (Allgemeinverstndlich), Art des Wertes) ####
    df_info_on_QI_indicators_2018 = pd.read_excel('C:/Users/User/Desktop/Info_on_quality_indicators_2018_en_translated.xlsx')
    df_info_on_QI_indicators_2018 = df_info_on_QI_indicators_2018.loc[:, ["Service_range", "Service_range_(generally_inderstood)", "Indicator_designation/KPI_designation", "Indicator_designation/KPI_designation_(generally_inderstood)", "Value_type", "ID"]]
    
    df_info_on_QI_indicators_2018 = df_info_on_QI_indicators_2018.rename(columns={"ID": 'ergebnis_id'})
    df_outer_infoQI = pd.merge(df_outer, df_info_on_QI_indicators_2018, on='ergebnis_id', how='left')
    df_outer_infoQI = df_outer_infoQI.sort_values(by=['count_ik_from_IT'], ascending=False, ignore_index=1)
    #############################################################################################################################
    return df_outer_infoQI



######################################## Raw and filter data###########################################################
df = pd.read_spss('C:/Users/User/Desktop/QI_en_translated.sav')
df0 = pd.read_spss('C:/Users/User/Desktop/Datensatz_4_IT_Report_2018.sav')
df_calculated_result = df.loc[:, ["ergebnis_id", "calculated_result"]]

rows_remove = ["U30", "U31", "U32", "U99", "D50", "D51", "D99"]
df_filter = df[df.qualitative_assessment_reporting_year.isin(rows_remove) == False]
#print("Size QI data: ", len(df))
#print(f"Size QI data without values {rows_remove} in column qualitative_assessment_reporting_year: ", len(df_filter))
#print("\n")

#print("Raw data")
df_raw = processed_data(df_filter, df0)


#display(df_raw)

df_filter = processed_data(df_filter, df0)
#print("Size new raw QI data: ", len(df_filter))
rows_remove = ["TKez", "Tkez"]
df_filter = df_filter[df_filter.Value_type.isin(rows_remove) == False]
df_filter = df_filter.sort_values(by=['count_ik_from_IT'], ascending=False, ignore_index=1)
#print(f"Size new raw QI data without values {rows_remove} in column Value_type: ", len(df_filter))
#print("\n")




df_filter = pd.merge(df_filter, df_calculated_result, on='ergebnis_id', how='left')
